cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.IR, cs.DL 

This paper deals with the application of deep learning models to medical imaging, specifically mammography. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of fine-tuning and histogram matching techniques, which are common in deep learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper deals with medical imaging (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) in the context of identifying breast cancer. Finally, the paper specifically mentions the use of deep learning models (cs.DL).
